Use cases:
==========
* flightsim:
   expects:     X/Y      Rudder   Throttle
   XBox:    Left-Stick   LT+RT    Right-Stick(rel)

* FPS:
   expects:  Mouse-X/Y   Walk-X/Y  Trigger
   XBox:    Left-Stick   RickStick Trigger(btn)

* 2D Jump Run (done)
   needs dpad first


